profile:
Vaultra Storage is a 100% Canadian owned and operated. The company is a one-stop storage solution, featuring self storage, pick up and delivery service, LAUFT coworking spaces and rental moving boxes. Each facility offers simple, seamless and secure storage solutions for all. Whether looking to store for business or personal use, Vaultra’s team will find the services that fit their customers best.

Vaultra self storage facilities offer convenient and secure locations, with units that range from traditional drive-up, indoor, heated, climate controlled to outdoor vehicle storage. Visit vaultrastorage.ca/self-storage to find a location nearby!

The pick up and delivery service, Vaultra Door to Door, is available throughout the GTA. It's simple: Vaultra movers pick up items and store them at a Vaultra facility. When the items are needed again, Vaultra Door to Door returns them! To see service areas, as well as the Door to Door storage plans available, visit d2d.vaultra.ca.

LAUFT coworking spaces are featured in Vaultra Storage's Toronto Castlefield and Ajax locations. Their state of the art facilities are perfect for business owners and/or entrepreneurs who want a space to work, while having their inventory right around the corner. Book a coworking space at lauft.work!

The rental moving box service, Vaultra CityBoxes, offers 27” x 17” x 12” bins that are stackable and reusable. First Vaultra CityBoxes delivers the bins. Then, clients pack, move and unpack. Afterwards, they pick up the bins! To see the service area and rent moving boxes, visit vaultrastorage.ca/bin-rental.

profile:
Welcome to All-Ways Moving Canada
***
All-Ways Moving & Storage is your best choice for an excellent quality, customer oriented moving company in Nova Scotia, Windsor, Halifax and the Annapolis Valley. All-ways Moving & Storage head office is located in Newport, Nova Scotia. We serve customers from all across Canada including but not limited to Windsor, Mount Uniacke, Wolfville, Hantsport, Berwick, Annapolis, Halifax, Dartmouth, and westward on to Toronto, Calgary, Vancouver and many other Canadian cities. 800 MILES IS AS FAR AS WE SERVICE.
***
Be assured your move is done right - Use All-Ways Moving & Storage and see & feel the difference.
***
Moving is an exciting time in people's lives. It often marks the start of a new adventure or opportunity. With a move comes a feeling of starting fresh and our mission is to help make that experience as easy as possible from the very beginning with a hassle free, reliable team of movers, the way moving should be - anywhere in Canada. We offer professional, caring and experienced moving services to transfer your belongings, allowing you to concentrate on the other aspects of your move.
***
Quick & Free Online Moving Estimate / Moving Quote
Use our Free Online form for a quick and free Moving Estimate / Moving Quote
Average within 5% on my estimates!!
***
All-ways Moving & Storage's top quality service is reflected in our repeat customers and referrals, whom always move with All-Ways Moving & Storage!
***
Moving across Canada: Moves originating in Halifax, Windsor (and local area), Annapolis Valley - Berwick, Wolfville (Acadia University), Mount Uniacke and more.
***
Other Canadian Cities: Moving to or from Toronto, or other Ontario Cities, Calgary, Edmonton, other Alberta locations, Vancouver and British Columbia's Lower Mainland, and other cities across Canada.
***
We specialize in moving Households within Canada. Contacting us and Estimate / Quotes are all FREE
